"If you choose a \"Numeric\" input, you should leave the points blank! It "
"will be filled in by the judges for speedrolling and such."
msgstr ""

#: competitors-settings.php:569
msgid ""
"There are three different possible scoreboards by default, corresponding to "
"what class the competitor will register to. A competitor can participate in "
"one class only. You can add classes, rolls etc. but keep in mind you can NOT "
"change the sequence later. Also, if you delete a class, all competitors will "
"be unavailable (but the data is retrievable). If more freedom is needed, let "
"me know, but keep in mind: Your favourite apps have thousands of developers "
"and cost billions! Not joking."
msgstr ""

